sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant W as Web UI
  participant A as FastAPI
  participant L as llama.cpp

  U->>W: Submit prompt
  W->>A: /chat (WebSocket) or /generate (HTTP)
  A->>L: Completion request
  L-->>A: Generated tokens
  A-->>W: Streamed response
  W-->>U: Render final answer
